<div class="rp-sidebar-section">
  <h3 class="rp-sidebar-title">Supported Files</h3>
  <ul class="rp-import-list">
    <li><strong>.md / .markdown</strong> - Markdown with optional frontmatter</li>
    <li><strong>.txt</strong> - Plain text (title from filename)</li>
    <li><strong>.zip</strong> - Archive containing multiple files</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="rp-sidebar-section">
  <h3 class="rp-sidebar-title">Frontmatter Fields</h3>
  <ul class="rp-import-list">
    <li><strong>title</strong> - Post title (required)</li>
    <li><strong>slug</strong> - URL slug (auto-generated if blank)</li>
    <li><strong>status</strong> - draft or published (default: draft)</li>
    <li><strong>published_at</strong> - Publish date (default: today)</li>
    <li><strong>author</strong> - Author name (case-insensitive match)</li>
    <li><strong>category</strong> - Category name (case-insensitive match)</li>
    <li><strong>tags</strong> - Comma-separated tag names</li>
    <li><strong>header_image</strong> - Relative path in zip or URL</li>
    <li><strong>meta_title</strong> - SEO title</li>
    <li><strong>meta_description</strong> - SEO description</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="rp-sidebar-section">
  <h3 class="rp-sidebar-title">Example Markdown</h3>
  <pre class="rp-code-block"><code>---
title: My Blog Post
